{"tid":647350,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實林峰有咩代表作？","createTime":"2018-04-29T18:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T17:40:00.000Z","uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c7959f89e47e4ada9dcc131eab227a41d7120f0f","tid":647350,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"口碑最好都係早期 （未造神時）<br />\n溏心風雲 1 同 2 同宜家嘅使徒行者<br />\n一係就係初出道時嘅尋秦記<br />\n<br />\n再數就要到二次出道既（整容完/整緊容嘅）<br />\n大唐雙龍傳 同 律政新人王<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢唱歌雖然係幾好 （tbb入邊佢認第二 冇人敢認第一 宜家更加係）<br />\n但係用演員把尺睇 佢唔似陳豪/林保咁多樣性/高汁 又唔似橡膠穎咁有親都係好角色<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實宜家睇返<br />\n少年四大名捕除咗馬明慢慢進化為實力派<br />\n其他三個仲係偶像派<br />\n如果林峰喺使徒行者嗰期肯留喺tbb轉轉路線 咁佢可能宜家已經係再發力期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700bc519af044ee97b825452211d3adc41a02805","tid":647350,"uid":124450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"我想嘅講嘅係<br />\n<br />\n林峰做完使徒行者食住個勢一定會有更加多嘅好角色好劇<br />\n煎pan都唔會上到位"},{"pid":"1425160c5d23e1fa3bacff91e7fba857fa086815","tid":647350,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"美味天皇？<br />\n不過依家都無人識佢啦"},{"pid":"37dc3c2b1f52393eb7eab89e84483cbee47934fe","tid":647350,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:44:00.000Z","msg":"新戲拍住韋家輝劉青雲, 年尾又開尋泰記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cc5a0f99a5ee1f12626e1541c6722096c41c7f","tid":647350,"uid":28007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:46:09.000Z","msg":"Let get wet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4943faf2e1f403b522e96bc8bf128170958e4cd","tid":647350,"uid":180035,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/024604_fbed88df5d1797e